WEBVTT

1
00:01:13.570 --> 00:01:15.570
<font color="#616161">I can't let you out, Hedwig.</font>

2
00:01:15.570 --> 00:01:18.570
<font color="#616161">I'm not allowed to use
magic outside of school.</font>

3
00:01:19.570 --> 00:01:23.570
<font color="#616161">~ Besides, if Uncle Vernon....
~ Harry Potter!</font>

4
00:01:25.570 --> 00:01:26.570
<font color="#616161">Now you've done it.</font>

5
00:01:31.570 --> 00:01:34.570
<font color="#616161">He's in there. Vernon?</font>

6
00:01:36.638 --> 00:01:40.434
<font color="#616161">I'm warning you, if you can't control that bloody bird, 
it'll have to go.</font>

7
00:01:40.976 --> 00:01:42.394
<font color="#616161">But she's bored.</font>

8
00:01:42.561 --> 00:01:47.065
<font color="#616161">If I could only let her
out for an hour or two.</font>

9
00:01:47.232 --> 00:01:51.195
<font color="#616161">So you can send secret messages to your freaky little friends? No, sir.</font>

10
00:01:51.361 --> 00:01:56.491
<font color="#616161">But I haven't had any messages from any of my friends.</font>

11
00:01:56.658 --> 00:01:58.327
<font color="#616161">Not one....</font>

12
00:01:58.744 --> 00:02:00.204
<font color="#616161">....all summer.</font>

13
00:02:00.370 --> 00:02:03.624
<font color="#616161">Who would want to be
friends with you?</font>

14
00:02:05.876 --> 00:02:08.337
<font color="#616161">I should think you'd be
a little more grateful.</font>

15
00:02:08.504 --> 00:02:12.007
<font color="#616161">We've raised you since you were a baby, given you the food 
off our table....</font>

16
00:02:12.174 --> 00:02:14.301
<font color="#616161">....even let you have
Dudley's second bedroom....</font>

17
00:02:14.468 --> 00:02:17.012
<font color="#616161">....purely out of the
goodness of our hearts.</font>

18
00:02:17.429 --> 00:02:19.681
<font color="#616161">Not now. It's for when
the Masons arrive.</font>

19
00:02:20.140 --> 00:02:23.185
<font color="#616161">Which should be any minute.</font>

20
00:02:23.852 --> 00:02:26.688
<font color="#616161">Now, let's go over our
schedule once again, shall we?</font>

21
00:02:26.855 --> 00:02:28.774
<font color="#616161">Petunia, when the Masons
arrive, you will be....?</font>

22
00:02:28.941 --> 00:02:32.653
<font color="#616161">In the lounge, waiting to welcome them graciously to our home.</font>

23
00:02:32.819 --> 00:02:36.740
<font color="#616161">~ Good. And, Dudley, you will be....?
~ I'll be waiting to open the door.</font>

24
00:02:36.907 --> 00:02:38.825
<font color="#616161">Excellent.</font>

25
00:02:43.372 --> 00:02:45.207
<font color="#616161">And you?</font>

26
00:02:45.791 --> 00:02:50.170
<font color="#616161">I'll be in my bedroom, making no noise and pretending that 
I don't exist.</font>

27
00:02:50.337 --> 00:02:52.047
<font color="#616161">Too right, you will.</font>

28
00:02:52.214 --> 00:02:55.717
<font color="#616161">With any luck, this could be the day I make the biggest 
deal of my career....</font>

29
00:02:55.884 --> 00:02:59.429
<font color="#616161">....and you will not mess it up.</font>

30
00:03:10.566 --> 00:03:15.404
<font color="#616161">Harry Potter, such
an honor it is.</font>

31
00:03:18.282 --> 00:03:23.203
<font color="#616161">~ Who are you? 
~ Dobby, sir. Dobby the house-elf.</font>

32
00:03:23.954 --> 00:03:25.289
<font color="#616161">Not to be rude or anything....</font>

33
00:03:25.455 --> 00:03:29.418
<font color="#616161">....but this isn't a great time for me to have a house-elf 
in my bedroom.</font>

34
00:03:29.585 --> 00:03:32.087
<font color="#616161">Yes, sir. Dobby understands.</font>

35
00:03:32.254 --> 00:03:35.382
<font color="#616161">It's just that Dobby has
come to tell you....</font>

36
00:03:35.549 --> 00:03:40.387
<font color="#616161">It is difficult, sir. Dobby wonders where to begin.</font>

37
00:03:40.554 --> 00:03:46.351
<font color="#616161">~ Why don't you sit down?
~ Sit down? Sit down?</font>

38
00:03:49.605 --> 00:03:54.109
<font color="#616161">Dobby, I'm sorry. I didn't mean to offend you or anything.</font>

39
00:03:54.276 --> 00:03:56.445
<font color="#616161">Offend Dobby?</font>

40
00:03:56.612 --> 00:03:58.947
<font color="#616161">Dobby has heard of
your greatness, sir....</font>

41
00:03:59.114 --> 00:04:04.912
<font color="#616161">....but never has he been asked to sit down by a wizard, 
like an equal.</font>

42
00:04:05.829 --> 00:04:08.457
<font color="#616161">You can't have met many
decent wizards then.</font>

43
00:04:08.624 --> 00:04:11.043
<font color="#616161">No, I haven't.</font>

44
00:04:11.210 --> 00:04:13.962
<font color="#616161">That was an awful thing to say.</font>

45
00:04:14.630 --> 00:04:18.091
<font color="#616161">~ Bad Dobby! Bad Dobby!
~ Stop, Dobby. Dobby, shush.</font>

46
00:04:18.258 --> 00:04:19.635
<font color="#616161">Dobby, please, stop.</font>

47
00:04:24.139 --> 00:04:26.767
<font color="#616161">Don't mind that.
It's just the cat.</font>

48
00:04:28.685 --> 00:04:33.232
<font color="#616161">~ Bad Dobby. 
~ Stop! Stop, Dobby. Please, be quiet.</font>

49
00:04:33.398 --> 00:04:35.692
<font color="#616161">Are you all right?</font>

50
00:04:36.443 --> 00:04:39.321
<font color="#616161">Dobby had to punish
himself, sir.</font>

51
00:04:39.488 --> 00:04:42.699
<font color="#616161">Dobby almost spoke ill
of his family, sir.</font>

52
00:04:42.866 --> 00:04:46.828
<font color="#616161">~ Your family? 
~ The wizard family Dobby serves, sir.</font>

53
00:04:46.995 --> 00:04:49.998
<font color="#616161">Dobby is bound to serve
one family forever.</font>

54
00:04:50.165 --> 00:04:52.709
<font color="#616161">If they ever knew Dobby was here....</font>

55
00:04:54.336 --> 00:05:00.133
<font color="#616161">But Dobby had to come. Dobby has to protect Harry Potter. 
To warn him.</font>

56
00:05:00.300 --> 00:05:02.594
<font color="#616161">Harry Potter must not go back....</font>

57
00:05:02.761 --> 00:05:07.474
<font color="#616161">....to Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry this year.</font>

58
00:05:07.641 --> 00:05:12.813
<font color="#616161">There is a plot, a plot to make most terrible things happen.</font>

59
00:05:12.980 --> 00:05:16.316
<font color="#616161">What terrible things?
Who's plotting them?</font>

60
00:05:17.192 --> 00:05:19.653
<font color="#616161">Can't say.</font>

61
00:05:20.112 --> 00:05:25.826
<font color="#616161">~ Okay, I understand. You can't say. 
~ Don't make me talk. L....</font>

62
00:05:27.244 --> 00:05:30.539
<font color="#616161">~ Dobby. Dobby, put the lamp down. 
~ Bad Dobby.</font>

63
00:05:30.706 --> 00:05:34.751
<font color="#616161">So when they arrive at the ninth hole....</font>

64
00:05:37.337 --> 00:05:39.923
<font color="#616161">Give me the lamp.</font>

65
00:05:41.633 --> 00:05:44.052
<font color="#616161">Dobby, stop!</font>

66
00:05:46.221 --> 00:05:49.224
<font color="#616161">~ Let me go.
~ Get in there and keep quiet.</font>

67
00:05:49.391 --> 00:05:53.437
<font color="#616161">~ What the devil are you doing up here? 
~ I was just....</font>

68
00:05:53.604 --> 00:05:56.356
<font color="#616161">You just ruined the punch line of my Japanese golfer joke.</font>

69
00:05:56.940 --> 00:05:58.358
<font color="#616161">Sorry.</font>

70
00:05:59.902 --> 00:06:03.989
<font color="#616161">One more sound and you'll wish you'd never been born, boy.</font>

71
00:06:04.156 --> 00:06:07.951
<font color="#616161">~ And fix that door.
~ Yes, sir.</font>

72
00:06:10.245 --> 00:06:11.872
<font color="#616161">See why I've got to go back?</font>

73
00:06:12.039 --> 00:06:15.792
<font color="#616161">I don't belong here. I belong in your world, at Hogwarts.</font>

74
00:06:15.959 --> 00:06:20.589
<font color="#616161">~ It's the only place I've got friends. 
~ Friends who don't write to Harry Potter?</font>

75
00:06:20.756 --> 00:06:23.675
<font color="#616161">Well, I expect they've been....</font>

76
00:06:23.842 --> 00:06:28.514
<font color="#616161">Hang on. How do you know my friends haven't been writing to me?</font>

77
00:06:28.931 --> 00:06:32.059
<font color="#616161">Harry Potter mustn't
be angry with Dobby.</font>

78
00:06:32.226 --> 00:06:36.438
<font color="#616161">Dobby hoped if Harry Potter thought his friends had forgotten him....</font>

79
00:06:36.605 --> 00:06:40.275
<font color="#616161">....Harry Potter might not want to go back to school, sir.</font>

80
00:06:41.109 --> 00:06:45.864
<font color="#616161">~ Give me those. Now.
~ No!</font>

81
00:06:58.168 --> 00:07:01.463
<font color="#616161">Dobby, get back here.</font>

82
00:07:04.633 --> 00:07:07.970
<font color="#616161">Dobby, please, no.</font>

83
00:07:08.136 --> 00:07:12.307
<font color="#616161">Harry Potter must say he's not going back to school.</font>

84
00:07:12.641 --> 00:07:15.102
<font color="#616161">I can't. Hogwarts is my home.</font>

85
00:07:15.769 --> 00:07:21.358
<font color="#616161">Then Dobby must do it, sir, for Harry Potter's own good.</font>

86
00:07:21.525 --> 00:07:26.530
<font color="#616161">It spread as far as the eye could see, all over the floor of 
this building.</font>

87
00:07:26.697 --> 00:07:28.657
<font color="#616161">One plumber said, "Look at all that water."</font>

88
00:07:28.824 --> 00:07:31.827
<font color="#616161">The second plumber said, "Yes, and that's just the top of it."</font>

89
00:07:43.589 --> 00:07:47.676
<font color="#616161">I'm so sorry. It's my nephew. He's very disturbed.</font>

90
00:07:47.843 --> 00:07:52.181
<font color="#616161">Meeting strangers upsets him. That's why I kept him upstairs.</font>

91
00:08:03.901 --> 00:08:06.361
<font color="#616161">You're never going
back to that school.</font>

92
00:08:06.528 --> 00:08:11.575
<font color="#616161">You're never going to see those freaky friends of yours again. Never!</font>

93
00:08:57.746 --> 00:08:58.872
<font color="#616161">Hiya, Harry.</font>

94
00:08:59.957 --> 00:09:04.419
<font color="#616161">Ron. Fred. George. What
are you all doing here?</font>

95
00:09:04.586 --> 00:09:08.465
<font color="#616161">Rescuing you, of course. Now, come on, get your trunk.</font>

96
00:09:14.680 --> 00:09:16.890
<font color="#616161">You better stand back.</font>

97
00:09:17.307 --> 00:09:19.434
<font color="#616161">Let's go.</font>

98
00:09:24.189 --> 00:09:26.108
<font color="#616161">~ What was that?
~ What was it?</font>

99
00:09:28.402 --> 00:09:30.612
<font color="#616161">Potter!</font>

100
00:09:30.779 --> 00:09:32.447
<font color="#616161">Dad, what's going on?</font>

101
00:09:35.701 --> 00:09:36.743
<font color="#616161">Go. Go. Go.</font>

102
00:09:36.910 --> 00:09:37.953
<font color="#616161">Dad, hurry up.</font>

103
00:09:39.788 --> 00:09:41.999
<font color="#616161">~ Come on.
~ Come on, Harry, hurry up.</font>

104
00:09:43.959 --> 00:09:45.794
<font color="#616161">Petunia, he's escaping!</font>

105
00:09:48.005 --> 00:09:49.506
<font color="#616161">~ I've got you, Harry.
~ Come here!</font>

106
00:09:49.965 --> 00:09:51.800
<font color="#616161">~ Let go of me!
~ No, boy!</font>

107
00:09:51.967 --> 00:09:54.970
<font color="#616161">You and that bloody pigeon aren't going anywhere.</font>

108
00:09:55.137 --> 00:09:56.763
<font color="#616161">~ Get off!
~ Drive!</font>

109
00:09:56.930 --> 00:09:58.807
<font color="#616161">~ Right.
~ Right!</font>

110
00:09:58.974 --> 00:10:00.642
<font color="#616161">No! No! No! No!</font>

111
00:10:05.022 --> 00:10:06.815
<font color="#616161">Dad!</font>

112
00:10:15.949 --> 00:10:17.451
<font color="#616161">Damn.</font>

113
00:10:21.580 --> 00:10:25.459
<font color="#616161">By the way, Harry, Happy Birthday.</font>

114
00:10:51.777 --> 00:10:53.570
<font color="#616161">Come on.</font>

115
00:10:56.281 --> 00:10:58.200
<font color="#616161">Okay, come on.</font>

116
00:10:59.034 --> 00:11:01.245
<font color="#616161">Okay, come on.</font>

117
00:11:09.461 --> 00:11:13.549
<font color="#616161">~ Think it'd be all right if we had some? 
~ Yeah, Mum will never know.</font>

118
00:11:30.232 --> 00:11:33.443
<font color="#616161">It's not much, but it's home.</font>

119
00:11:33.610 --> 00:11:35.904
<font color="#616161">I think it's brilliant.</font>

120
00:11:36.655 --> 00:11:40.409
<font color="#616161">Where have you been?</font>

121
00:11:40.826 --> 00:11:43.871
<font color="#616161">Harry, how wonderful
to see you, dear.</font>

122
00:11:44.037 --> 00:11:47.624
<font color="#616161">Beds empty. No note. Car gone.</font>

123
00:11:47.791 --> 00:11:50.794
<font color="#616161">You could have died. You
could have been seen.</font>

124
00:11:51.378 --> 00:11:54.006
<font color="#616161">Of course, I don't blame
you, Harry, dear.</font>

125
00:11:54.173 --> 00:11:57.217
<font color="#616161">They were starving him, Mum. There were bars on his window.</font>

126
00:11:57.384 --> 00:12:02.139
<font color="#616161">Well, you best hope I don't put bars on your window, Ronald Weasley.</font>

127
00:12:02.306 --> 00:12:04.433
<font color="#616161">Come on, Harry, time for
a spot of breakfast.</font>

128
00:12:05.601 --> 00:12:08.353
<font color="#616161">Here we are, Harry.
Now, tuck in.</font>

129
00:12:08.520 --> 00:12:12.107
<font color="#616161">That's it. There we go.</font>

130
00:12:12.608 --> 00:12:16.111
<font color="#616161">~ Mummy, have you seen my jumper?
~ Yes, dear, it was on the cat.</font>

131
00:12:16.695 --> 00:12:18.363
<font color="#616161">Hello.</font>

132
00:12:22.701 --> 00:12:24.077
<font color="#616161">What did I do?</font>

133
00:12:24.244 --> 00:12:28.832
<font color="#616161">Ginny. She's been talking about you all summer. A bit annoying, really.</font>

134
00:12:28.999 --> 00:12:31.627
<font color="#616161">~ Morning, Weasleys.
~ Morning, Dad.</font>

135
00:12:32.586 --> 00:12:36.340
<font color="#616161">~ What a night. Nine raids. Nine! 
~ Raids?</font>

136
00:12:36.798 --> 00:12:40.469
<font color="#616161">Dad works in the Ministry of Magic, in the Misuse of 
Muggle Artifacts Office.</font>

137
00:12:40.802 --> 00:12:43.972
<font color="#616161">Dad loves Muggles, thinks  they're fascinating.</font>

138
00:12:44.139 --> 00:12:46.350
<font color="#616161">Well, now.</font>

139
00:12:48.268 --> 00:12:49.478
<font color="#616161">And who are you?</font>

140
00:12:50.270 --> 00:12:53.815
<font color="#616161">Sorry, sir. I'm Harry, sir. Harry Potter.</font>

141
00:12:54.233 --> 00:12:57.110
<font color="#616161">Good Lord. Are you really?</font>

142
00:12:57.653 --> 00:13:01.990
<font color="#616161">Well, Ron has told us all about you, of course. When did he get here?</font>

143
00:13:02.157 --> 00:13:03.659
<font color="#616161">This morning.</font>

144
00:13:04.076 --> 00:13:09.039
<font color="#616161">Your sons flew that enchanted car of yours to Surrey and 
back last night.</font>

145
00:13:09.289 --> 00:13:12.668
<font color="#616161">Did you really? How did it go?</font>

146
00:13:12.835 --> 00:13:17.673
<font color="#616161">I mean.... That was very wrong indeed, boys. Very wrong of you.</font>

147
00:13:19.007 --> 00:13:22.845
<font color="#616161">Now, Harry, you must
know all about Muggles.</font>

148
00:13:23.095 --> 00:13:27.140
<font color="#616161">Tell me, what exactly is the function of a rubber duck?</font>

149
00:13:31.728 --> 00:13:34.481
<font color="#616161">Well, that'll be
Errol with the post.</font>

150
00:13:40.237 --> 00:13:43.031
<font color="#616161">Fetch it, will you, Percy, please?</font>

151
00:13:43.365 --> 00:13:46.577
<font color="#616161">~ Errol.
~ He's always doing that.</font>

152
00:13:48.245 --> 00:13:52.207
<font color="#616161">Look, it's our Hogwarts letters. They've sent us Harry's as well.</font>

153
00:13:52.374 --> 00:13:55.419
<font color="#616161">Dumbledore must know you're here. Doesn't miss a trick, 
that man.</font>

154
00:13:55.586 --> 00:13:57.546
<font color="#616161">~ No.
~ This lot won't come cheap.</font>

155
00:13:57.713 --> 00:14:02.050
<font color="#616161">~ The spell books alone are expensive. 
~ We'll manage.</font>

156
00:14:02.759 --> 00:14:07.014
<font color="#616161">There's only one place we're going to get all of this. Diagon Alley.</font>

157
00:14:08.265 --> 00:14:09.641
<font color="#616161">Right.</font>

158
00:14:09.808 --> 00:14:11.935
<font color="#616161">Here we are, Harry.
You go first, dear.</font>

159
00:14:12.102 --> 00:14:15.063
<font color="#616161">But Harry's never traveled by Floo powder before, Mum.</font>

160
00:14:15.230 --> 00:14:16.273
<font color="#616161">Floo powder?</font>

161
00:14:16.440 --> 00:14:20.736
<font color="#616161">You go first, Ron, so that Harry can see how it's done. Yes.</font>

162
00:14:21.361 --> 00:14:23.238
<font color="#616161">In you go.</font>

163
00:14:23.780 --> 00:14:25.282
<font color="#616161">That's it.</font>

164
00:14:28.785 --> 00:14:30.496
<font color="#616161">Diagon Alley.</font>

165
00:14:36.543 --> 00:14:40.047
<font color="#616161">You see? It's quite easy, dear. Don't be afraid. Come on.</font>

166
00:14:41.798 --> 00:14:43.008
<font color="#616161">Come on.</font>

167
00:14:43.175 --> 00:14:46.386
<font color="#616161">In you go. That's it.
Mind your head.</font>

168
00:14:46.553 --> 00:14:49.973
<font color="#616161">That's right. Now,
take your Floo powder.</font>

169
00:14:51.517 --> 00:14:53.977
<font color="#616161">That's it, very good.</font>

170
00:14:54.144 --> 00:14:58.482
<font color="#616161">Now, don't forget to speak very, very clearly.</font>

171
00:15:00.317 --> 00:15:02.694
<font color="#616161">Diagonally.</font>

172
00:15:09.159 --> 00:15:11.578
<font color="#616161">~ What did he say, dear?
~ Diagonally.</font>

173
00:15:11.745 --> 00:15:12.830
<font color="#616161">I thought he did.</font>

174
00:16:37.831 --> 00:16:43.129
<font color="#616161">~ Not lost, are you, my dear? 
~ I'm fine, thank you. I was just going....</font>

175
00:16:44.296 --> 00:16:48.800
<font color="#616161">Come with us. We'll help
you find your way back.</font>

176
00:16:49.343 --> 00:16:51.678
<font color="#616161">~ No. Please....
~ Harry?</font>

177
00:16:51.845 --> 00:16:52.930
<font color="#616161">Hagrid!</font>

178
00:16:53.096 --> 00:16:56.099
<font color="#616161">What do you think you're
doing down here? Come on.</font>

179
00:17:01.897 --> 00:17:07.152
<font color="#616161">You're a mess, Harry. Skulking around Knockturn Alley? Dodgy place.</font>

180
00:17:07.319 --> 00:17:11.323
<font color="#616161">Don't want no one to see you there. People will think you're up 
to no good.</font>

181
00:17:11.490 --> 00:17:13.742
<font color="#616161">I was lost, I....</font>

182
00:17:13.909 --> 00:17:16.870
<font color="#616161">Hang on. What were you
doing down there then?</font>

183
00:17:17.037 --> 00:17:22.167
<font color="#616161">Me? I was.... I was looking for Flesh-Eating Slug Repellent.</font>

184
00:17:22.334 --> 00:17:25.254
<font color="#616161">They're ruining all
the school cabbages.</font>

185
00:17:30.676 --> 00:17:32.845
<font color="#616161">Harry. Hagrid.</font>

186
00:17:33.053 --> 00:17:34.471
<font color="#616161">Hello, Hermione.</font>

187
00:17:34.847 --> 00:17:37.474
<font color="#616161">~ It's so good to see you.
~ It's great to see you too.</font>

188
00:17:38.141 --> 00:17:40.727
<font color="#616161">What did you do to your glasses?</font>

189
00:17:40.894 --> 00:17:43.772
<font color="#616161">Oculus Reparo.</font>

190
00:17:47.234 --> 00:17:49.987
<font color="#616161">I definitely need to
remember that one.</font>

191
00:17:50.153 --> 00:17:53.866
<font color="#616161">You'll be all right now then,
Harry? Right. I'll leave you to it.</font>

192
00:17:54.032 --> 00:17:55.492
<font color="#616161">~ Okay, bye.
~ Thank you. Bye.</font>

193
00:17:55.784 --> 00:17:57.661
<font color="#616161">Come on, everyone's
been so worried.</font>

194
00:18:08.380 --> 00:18:09.506
<font color="#616161">Harry.</font>

195
00:18:09.673 --> 00:18:12.885
<font color="#616161">Thank goodness. We'd hoped you'd only gone one grate too far.</font>

196
00:18:13.051 --> 00:18:15.888
<font color="#616161">Ladies and gentlemen,
Mr. Gilderoy Lockhart.</font>

197
00:18:16.054 --> 00:18:18.348
<font color="#616161">Here he is.</font>

198
00:18:22.352 --> 00:18:23.979
<font color="#616161">Mum fancies him.</font>

199
00:18:24.146 --> 00:18:27.399
<font color="#616161">Make way there, please. Let me by, madam. Thank you.</font>

200
00:18:27.608 --> 00:18:31.028
<font color="#616161">Excuse me, little girl. This is for the Daily Prophet.</font>

201
00:18:35.199 --> 00:18:38.076
<font color="#616161">It can't be. Harry Potter?</font>

202
00:18:39.620 --> 00:18:41.497
<font color="#616161">Harry Potter!</font>

203
00:18:41.663 --> 00:18:42.873
<font color="#616161">Excuse me, madam.</font>

204
00:18:44.875 --> 00:18:48.712
<font color="#616161">Nice big smile, Harry. Together, you and I rate the front page.</font>

205
00:18:48.879 --> 00:18:52.049
<font color="#616161">Ladies and gentlemen, what an extraordinary moment this is.</font>

206
00:18:52.466 --> 00:18:55.636
<font color="#616161">When young Harry stepped into Flourish and Blotts this morning....</font>

207
00:18:55.802 --> 00:18:59.890
<font color="#616161">....to purchase my
autobiography, Magical Me....</font>

208
00:19:03.393 --> 00:19:06.271
<font color="#616161">....which, incidentally, is currently celebrating....</font>

209
00:19:06.438 --> 00:19:11.276
<font color="#616161">....its 27th week atop the Daily Prophet bestseller list....</font>

210
00:19:11.443 --> 00:19:15.948
<font color="#616161">....he had no idea that he would, in fact, be leaving....</font>

211
00:19:17.115 --> 00:19:22.037
<font color="#616161">....with my entire
collected works....</font>

212
00:19:22.621 --> 00:19:24.832
<font color="#616161">....free of charge.</font>

213
00:19:27.000 --> 00:19:29.253
<font color="#616161">Now, ladies?</font>

214
00:19:29.461 --> 00:19:32.589
<font color="#616161">Harry, now you give me those, and I'll get them signed.</font>

215
00:19:32.756 --> 00:19:36.260
<font color="#616161">All of you wait outside.
That's it.</font>

216
00:19:45.561 --> 00:19:48.063
<font color="#616161">I'll bet you loved that,
didn't you, Potter?</font>

217
00:19:48.230 --> 00:19:52.734
<font color="#616161">Famous Harry Potter. Can't go into a bookshop without making 
the front page.</font>

218
00:19:53.360 --> 00:19:55.070
<font color="#616161">Leave him alone.</font>

219
00:19:55.237 --> 00:19:58.740
<font color="#616161">Look, Potter. You've got
yourself a girlfriend.</font>

220
00:19:58.907 --> 00:20:02.953
<font color="#616161">Now, now, Draco, play nicely.</font>

221
00:20:03.370 --> 00:20:04.580
<font color="#616161">Mr. Potter.</font>

222
00:20:07.040 --> 00:20:11.003
<font color="#616161">Lucius Malfoy. We meet at last.</font>

223
00:20:11.170 --> 00:20:13.380
<font color="#616161">Forgive me.</font>

224
00:20:14.756 --> 00:20:16.800
<font color="#616161">Your scar is legend.</font>

225
00:20:17.342 --> 00:20:19.595
<font color="#616161">As, of course, is the
wizard who gave it to you.</font>

226
00:20:19.928 --> 00:20:22.097
<font color="#616161">Voldemort killed my parents.</font>

227
00:20:24.183 --> 00:20:27.644
<font color="#616161">He was nothing more
than a murderer.</font>

228
00:20:28.687 --> 00:20:31.607
<font color="#616161">You must be very brave
to mention his name.</font>

229
00:20:32.274 --> 00:20:33.609
<font color="#616161">Or very foolish.</font>

230
00:20:34.026 --> 00:20:37.571
<font color="#616161">Fear of a name only increases fear of the thing itself.</font>

231
00:20:39.156 --> 00:20:42.451
<font color="#616161">And you must be Miss Granger.</font>

232
00:20:45.287 --> 00:20:49.583
<font color="#616161">Yes, Draco has told me all about you. And your parents.</font>

233
00:20:54.213 --> 00:20:57.674
<font color="#616161">Muggles, aren't they?</font>

234
00:21:00.636 --> 00:21:05.724
<font color="#616161">Let me see. Red hair,
vacant expressions....</font>

235
00:21:07.142 --> 00:21:10.479
<font color="#616161">....tatty, secondhand book.</font>

236
00:21:10.687 --> 00:21:14.024
<font color="#616161">You must be the Weasleys.</font>

237
00:21:14.483 --> 00:21:16.485
<font color="#616161">It's mad in here.
Let's go outside.</font>

238
00:21:16.652 --> 00:21:20.364
<font color="#616161">~ Well, well, well.
~ Weasley senior. ~ Lucius.</font>

239
00:21:20.572 --> 00:21:25.244
<font color="#616161">Busy time at the Ministry, Arthur, all those extra raids?</font>

240
00:21:25.410 --> 00:21:27.746
<font color="#616161">I do hope they're
paying you overtime....</font>

241
00:21:27.913 --> 00:21:31.083
<font color="#616161">....but judging by the state of this, I'd say not.</font>

242
00:21:32.876 --> 00:21:36.630
<font color="#616161">What's the use in being a disgrace to the name of wizard....</font>

243
00:21:36.797 --> 00:21:38.882
<font color="#616161">....if they don't even
pay you well for it?</font>

244
00:21:39.174 --> 00:21:44.179
<font color="#616161">We have a very different idea about what disgraces the name of 
wizard, Malfoy.</font>

245
00:21:44.429 --> 00:21:46.223
<font color="#616161">Clearly.</font>

246
00:21:48.308 --> 00:21:52.020
<font color="#616161">Associating with Muggles.</font>

247
00:21:56.233 --> 00:22:00.821
<font color="#616161">And I thought your family could sink no lower.</font>

248
00:22:04.116 --> 00:22:06.910
<font color="#616161">I'll see you at work.</font>

249
00:22:11.081 --> 00:22:13.417
<font color="#616161">See you at school.

250
00:22:21.258 --> 00:22:23.927
<font color="#616161">~ 10:58, come on. 
~ The train will be leaving any moment.</font>

251
00:22:24.094 --> 00:22:27.389
<font color="#616161">Fred, George, Percy, you first.</font>

252
00:22:32.978 --> 00:22:34.605
<font color="#616161">Okay.</font>

253
00:22:40.652 --> 00:22:42.404
<font color="#616161">After you, dear.</font>

254
00:22:44.573 --> 00:22:47.784
<font color="#616161">Come on, Ginny, we'll
get you a seat. Hurry.</font>

255
00:22:49.077 --> 00:22:51.163
<font color="#616161">Let's go.</font>

256
00:23:05.093 --> 00:23:08.263
<font color="#616161">~ What do you two think you're doing? 
~ Sorry.</font>

257
00:23:08.680 --> 00:23:11.683
<font color="#616161">Lost control of the trolley.</font>

258
00:23:13.018 --> 00:23:15.354
<font color="#616161">~ Why can't we get through?
~ I don't know.</font>

259
00:23:15.521 --> 00:23:18.899
<font color="#616161">The gateway has sealed
itself for some reason.</font>

260
00:23:20.275 --> 00:23:24.196
<font color="#616161">The train leaves at exactly 11:00. We've missed it.</font>

261
00:23:24.363 --> 00:23:27.741
<font color="#616161">Harry, if we can't get through....</font>

262
00:23:28.033 --> 00:23:30.702
<font color="#616161">....maybe Mum and Dad
can't get back.</font>

263
00:23:31.662 --> 00:23:35.123
<font color="#616161">Maybe we should just go
and wait by the car.</font>

264
00:23:36.166 --> 00:23:37.501
<font color="#616161">The car.</font>

265
00:23:49.012 --> 00:23:51.181
<font color="#616161">Ron, I should tell you....</font>

266
00:23:51.348 --> 00:23:55.143
<font color="#616161">....most Muggles aren't accustomed to seeing a flying car.</font>

267
00:23:55.310 --> 00:23:56.395
<font color="#616161">Right.</font>

268
00:23:56.687 --> 00:23:57.729
<font color="#616161">Okay.</font>

269
00:24:15.038 --> 00:24:18.333
<font color="#616161">Oh, no! The Invisibility
Booster must be faulty.</font>

270
00:24:18.792 --> 00:24:21.920
<font color="#616161">Come on, then. Let's go lower. We need to find the train.</font>

271
00:24:22.087 --> 00:24:23.380
<font color="#616161">Okay.</font>

272
00:24:34.308 --> 00:24:36.351
<font color="#616161">All we need to do is
catch up with the train.</font>

273
00:24:36.518 --> 00:24:38.187
<font color="#616161">We can't be far behind.</font>

274
00:24:40.189 --> 00:24:42.900
<font color="#616161">~ Do you hear that?
~ We must be getting close.</font>

275
00:24:43.275 --> 00:24:45.444
<font color="#616161">Hold on.</font>

276
00:25:11.762 --> 00:25:13.931
<font color="#616161">Harry!</font>

277
00:25:16.558 --> 00:25:18.393
<font color="#616161">Hold on!</font>

278
00:25:21.730 --> 00:25:24.233
<font color="#616161">Take my hand!</font>

279
00:25:28.487 --> 00:25:29.738
<font color="#616161">Hold on!</font>

280
00:25:29.905 --> 00:25:33.492
<font color="#616161">I'm trying. Your hand's all sweaty.</font>

281
00:25:46.088 --> 00:25:49.383
<font color="#616161">~ I think we found the train.
~ Yeah.</font>

282
00:26:06.066 --> 00:26:07.317
<font color="#616161">Welcome home.</font>

283
00:26:23.458 --> 00:26:24.668
<font color="#616161">Up! Up!</font>

284
00:26:25.627 --> 00:26:27.796
<font color="#616161">It's not working!</font>

285
00:26:31.717 --> 00:26:34.303
<font color="#616161">Up! Ron, mind that tree!</font>

286
00:26:37.556 --> 00:26:39.683
<font color="#616161">Stop! Stop! Stop!</font>

287
00:27:02.789 --> 00:27:07.419
<font color="#616161">~ My wand. Look at my wand. 
~ Be thankful it's not your neck.</font>

288
00:27:09.046 --> 00:27:12.049
<font color="#616161">~ What's happening?
~ I don't know.</font>

289
00:27:47.501 --> 00:27:49.628
<font color="#616161">Come on, go! Fast!</font>

290
00:28:23.996 --> 00:28:26.790
<font color="#616161">Scabbers, you're okay.</font>

291
00:28:28.292 --> 00:28:30.335
<font color="#616161">The car!</font>

292
00:28:45.809 --> 00:28:47.644
<font color="#616161">Dad's gonna kill me.</font>

293
00:28:56.195 --> 00:28:58.530
<font color="#616161">See you, Hedwig.</font>

294
00:28:59.865 --> 00:29:02.201
<font color="#616161">So a house-elf shows up in my bedroom....</font>

295
00:29:02.367 --> 00:29:05.329
<font color="#616161">....we can't get through the barrier to platform 93/4....</font>

296
00:29:05.496 --> 00:29:08.749
<font color="#616161">....we almost get killed by a tree....</font>

297
00:29:08.916 --> 00:29:12.461
<font color="#616161">Clearly someone doesn't
want me here this year.</font>

298
00:29:16.048 --> 00:29:19.009
<font color="#616161">Well, take a good look, lads.</font>

299
00:29:19.176 --> 00:29:23.096
<font color="#616161">This night might well be the last you spend in this castle.</font>

300
00:29:25.891 --> 00:29:29.394
<font color="#616161">Oh, dear, we are in trouble.</font>

301
00:29:29.686 --> 00:29:35.059
<font color="#616161">You were seen by no less
than seven Muggles.</font>

302
00:29:36.318 --> 00:29:39.071
<font color="#616161">Do you have any idea
how serious this is?</font>

303
00:29:39.780 --> 00:29:43.617
<font color="#616161">You have risked the
exposure of our world.</font>

304
00:29:44.284 --> 00:29:47.204
<font color="#616161">Not to mention the damage you inflicted on a Whomping Willow....</font>

305
00:29:47.371 --> 00:29:50.541
<font color="#616161">....that's been on these grounds since before you were born.</font>

306
00:29:50.999 --> 00:29:54.545
<font color="#616161">Honestly, Professor Snape, I think it did more damage to us.</font>

307
00:29:54.711 --> 00:29:55.879
<font color="#616161">Silence.</font>

308
00:29:57.881 --> 00:30:03.263
<font color="#616161">I assure you that were you in Slytherin, and your fate rested 
with me....</font>

309
00:30:04.429 --> 00:30:08.225
<font color="#616161">....the both of you would be on the train home tonight.</font>

310
00:30:09.393 --> 00:30:11.645
<font color="#616161">~ As it is....
~ They are not.</font>

311
00:30:13.856 --> 00:30:17.901
<font color="#616161">Professor Dumbledore.
Professor McGonagall.</font>

312
00:30:18.277 --> 00:30:19.778
<font color="#616161">Headmaster....</font>

313
00:30:19.945 --> 00:30:24.741
<font color="#616161">....these boys have flouted the Decree for the Restriction 
of Underage Wizardry.</font>

314
00:30:24.908 --> 00:30:28.829
<font color="#616161">~ As such.... 
~ I am well aware of our bylaws....</font>

315
00:30:28.996 --> 00:30:31.874
<font color="#616161">....having written quite
a few of them myself.</font>

316
00:30:32.249 --> 00:30:35.460
<font color="#616161">However, as head of
Gryffindor house....</font>

317
00:30:35.627 --> 00:30:40.632
<font color="#616161">....it is for Professor McGonagall to determine the appropriate action.</font>

318
00:30:41.091 --> 00:30:43.260
<font color="#616161">We'll go and get our stuff, then.</font>

319
00:30:43.427 --> 00:30:45.888
<font color="#616161">What are you talking about, Mr. Weasley?</font>

320
00:30:46.054 --> 00:30:48.265
<font color="#616161">You're going to expel us, aren't you?</font>

321
00:30:49.808 --> 00:30:52.936
<font color="#616161">Not today, Mr. Weasley....</font>

322
00:30:53.103 --> 00:30:58.108
<font color="#616161">....but I must impress on both of you the seriousness of what 
you have done.</font>

323
00:30:58.650 --> 00:31:03.280
<font color="#616161">I will be writing to your families tonight, and you will both receive detention.</font>

324
00:31:27.638 --> 00:31:30.140
<font color="#616161">Morning, everyone.</font>

325
00:31:30.807 --> 00:31:33.352
<font color="#616161">~ Good morning, everyone. 
~ Good morning, Professor Sprout.</font>

326
00:31:33.519 --> 00:31:37.814
<font color="#616161">Welcome to Greenhouse Three, second years. Gather around, everyone.</font>

327
00:31:37.981 --> 00:31:40.817
<font color="#616161">Today we're going to re-pot Mandrakes.</font>

328
00:31:40.984 --> 00:31:44.988
<font color="#616161">Who here can tell me the
properties of the Mandrake root?</font>

329
00:31:45.155 --> 00:31:46.990
<font color="#616161">Yes, Miss Granger?</font>

330
00:31:47.157 --> 00:31:49.493
<font color="#616161">Mandrake, or Mandragora....</font>

331
00:31:49.660 --> 00:31:54.665
<font color="#616161">....is used to return those who have been Petrified to their original state.</font>

332
00:31:54.832 --> 00:31:59.837
<font color="#616161">It's also dangerous. The Mandrake's cry is fatal to anyone who 
hears it.</font>

333
00:32:00.003 --> 00:32:02.840
<font color="#616161">Excellent. Ten points to Gryffindor.</font>

334
00:32:03.006 --> 00:32:05.676
<font color="#616161">As our Mandrakes are 
still only seedlings....</font>

335
00:32:05.843 --> 00:32:07.761
<font color="#616161">....their cries won't kill you yet.</font>

336
00:32:07.928 --> 00:32:11.723
<font color="#616161">But they could knock you out for hours, which is why I have 
given you earmuffs.....</font>

337
00:32:11.890 --> 00:32:13.392
<font color="#616161">....for auditory protection.</font>

338
00:32:13.559 --> 00:32:18.021
<font color="#616161">So could you please put them on, right away? Quickly.</font>

339
00:32:18.188 --> 00:32:20.983
<font color="#616161">Flaps tight down, and
watch me closely.</font>

340
00:32:21.149 --> 00:32:24.152
<font color="#616161">You grasp your Mandrake firmly.</font>

341
00:32:24.319 --> 00:32:27.322
<font color="#616161">You pull it sharply
up out of the pot.</font>

342
00:32:31.577 --> 00:32:33.495
<font color="#616161">Got it? And....</font>

343
00:32:33.704 --> 00:32:35.831
<font color="#616161">....now you dunk it down
into the other pot....</font>

344
00:32:35.998 --> 00:32:40.711
<font color="#616161">....and pour a little sprinkling of soil to keep him warm.</font>

345
00:32:44.339 --> 00:32:47.551
<font color="#616161">Longbottom's been
neglecting his earmuffs.</font>

346
00:32:47.968 --> 00:32:52.014
<font color="#616161">~ No, ma'am, he's just fainted. 
~ Yes, well, just leave him there.</font>

347
00:32:52.389 --> 00:32:55.934
<font color="#616161">Right, on we go. Plenty
of pots to go around.</font>

348
00:32:56.101 --> 00:32:59.688
<font color="#616161">Grasp your Mandrake and pull it up.</font>

349
00:33:14.620 --> 00:33:18.415
<font color="#616161">~ There's Nearly Headless Nick.
~ Hello, Percy, Miss Clearwater.</font>

350
00:33:18.582 --> 00:33:21.126
<font color="#616161">Hello, Sir Nicholas.</font>

351
00:33:32.596 --> 00:33:35.891
<font color="#616161">Say it. I'm doomed.</font>

352
00:33:36.725 --> 00:33:38.644
<font color="#616161">~ You're doomed.
~ Hi, Harry.</font>

353
00:33:40.896 --> 00:33:43.607
<font color="#616161">I'm Colin Creevey. I'm
in Gryffindor too.</font>

354
00:33:43.774 --> 00:33:45.400
<font color="#616161">Hi, Colin. Nice to meet you.</font>

355
00:33:45.943 --> 00:33:47.778
<font color="#616161">Ron, is that your owl?</font>

356
00:34:02.501 --> 00:34:05.170
<font color="#616161">Bloody bird's a menace.</font>

357
00:34:09.383 --> 00:34:10.884
<font color="#616161">Oh, no.</font>

358
00:34:11.051 --> 00:34:14.513
<font color="#616161">Look, everyone. Weasley's got himself a Howler.</font>

359
00:34:15.973 --> 00:34:21.228
<font color="#616161">Go on, Ron. I ignored one from my gran once. It was horrible.</font>

360
00:34:28.402 --> 00:34:30.279
<font color="#616161">Ronald Weasley!</font>

361
00:34:32.906 --> 00:34:38.096
<font color="#616161">How dare you steal that car! I am absolutely disgusted!</font>

362
00:34:39.288 --> 00:34:41.874
<font color="#616161">Your father's now facing
an inquiry at work....</font>

363
00:34:42.040 --> 00:34:44.418
<font color="#616161">....nd it's entirely your fault!</font>

364
00:34:44.877 --> 00:34:48.755
<font color="#616161">If you put another toe out of line....</font>

365
00:34:48.922 --> 00:34:52.176
<font color="#616161">....we'll bring you straight home!</font>

366
00:34:52.968 --> 00:34:56.471
<font color="#616161">And, Ginny, dear, congratulations on making Gryffindor.</font>

367
00:34:56.638 --> 00:35:00.350
<font color="#616161">Your father and I are so proud.</font>

368
00:35:18.619 --> 00:35:24.042
<font color="#616161">Let me introduce you to your new Defense Against the Dark Arts teacher.</font>

369
00:35:25.209 --> 00:35:26.752
<font color="#616161">Me.</font>

370
00:35:26.919 --> 00:35:29.463
<font color="#616161">Gilderoy Lockhart....</font>

371
00:35:29.630 --> 00:35:32.925
<font color="#616161">....Order of Merlin, Third Class....</font>

372
00:35:33.091 --> 00:35:36.428
<font color="#616161">....honorary member of the Dark Force Defense League....</font>

373
00:35:36.595 --> 00:35:39.515
<font color="#616161">....and five times winner....</font>

374
00:35:39.848 --> 00:35:45.729
<font color="#616161">....of Witch Weekly's
Most-Charming-Smile Award.</font>

375
00:35:46.104 --> 00:35:47.606
<font color="#616161">But I don't talk about that.</font>

376
00:35:47.773 --> 00:35:52.319
<font color="#616161">I didn't get rid of the Bandon Banshee by smiling at him.</font>

377
00:35:56.073 --> 00:35:58.909
<font color="#616161">Now, be warned.</font>

378
00:35:59.201 --> 00:36:01.245
<font color="#616161">It is my job to arm you....</font>

379
00:36:01.411 --> 00:36:06.750
<font color="#616161">....against the foulest
creatures known to wizardkind.</font>

380
00:36:07.584 --> 00:36:11.171
<font color="#616161">You may find yourselves facing your worst fears in this room.</font>

381
00:36:11.338 --> 00:36:15.384
<font color="#616161">Know only that no harm can befall you whilst I am here.</font>

